<h1>Information on Diseases and Medical Conditions</h1>
<p>&nbsp;Health by Nick is an educational medical website focused on providing evidence-based information about diseases, medical conditions, pharmaceutical treatments, and a wide range of health-related topics. The content is written, reviewed, and regularly updated by Nicholas Smith, PharmD, BCPS, a Board Certified Pharmacotherapy Specialist. The website is designed to help readers better understand serious medical conditions through carefully researched material that aligns with current clinical standards and peer-reviewed medical literature. All information is intended for general educational purposes and should not be considered professional medical advice, diagnosis, or treatment. Readers are encouraged to consult licensed healthcare professionals before making any decisions regarding medications, therapies, or treatment plans. The website also emphasizes that no doctor-patient or pharmacist-patient relationship is created through the use of its content and that medical emergencies require immediate professional attention.</p>
